  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of the study is to evaluate clinical and radiographic outcomes in patients undergone
      all-arthroscopic autologous matrix induced chondrogenesis for symptomatic osteochondral talar
      lesions
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
